The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning, specifically in the context of microcontrollers with limited memory and compute capability. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of a dataset, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
